<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1198782-i-read-the-majority-of-this-book-up-to">I read the majority of this book , up to around the ancestry letters, and drifted off to read Sue Klebold&#39;s memoir. Is it worth returning to?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1198782'><a id="like_count_community_question_1198782" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1198782?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F3086160-the-hour-i-first-believed">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1198782-i-read-the-majority-of-this-book-up-to">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1198782-i-read-the-majority-of-this-book-up-to">See all 6 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
