<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/81787422-deirdre"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/81787422-deirdre">Deirdre</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
It is worth finishing. The ancestry letters dragged the story out but I feel that it does help in the transformation of the Caelum. 
</span>
</div>
